title: Yuuwaku Flash
sinopse:
It hurts, it hurts, my chest hurts!

In front of the lenses, my heart becomes bare...

Even though she became a model, high school student Koyuki doesn't know how to smile. After meeting the photographer Nanba, Koyuki's fate started changing.

(Source: Chibi Manga)

Included one-shots: Jikken Sasete yo, Papa Kinsei First Love Bangai-hen
